These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, purple
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower
2 different pets are kept: ferret, snake
There are 2 different nationalities: french, british
1. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the british##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Color       | purple       | green |
| Flower         | sunflower | rose  |
| Pet       | snake    | ferret    |
| Nationality   | british       | french      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: whist, scrabble
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, pink
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, nigerian
1. the person who likes white is on the right of the russian##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Game      | scrabble     | whist |
| Pet           | hedgehog | dog      |
| Color   | pink  | white      |
| Nationality         | russian | nigerian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, american
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, dahlia
City: venice, london
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, gardening
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the american##1
2. the thai is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Nationality      | thai | american  |
| Flower          | daffodil    | dahlia   |
| City   | london  | venice   |
| Hobby     | gardening     | traveling |

