.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, thriller
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, april
City: marseilles, new-york
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, orchid
1. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Movie-Genre      | drama       | thriller |
| Birthday          | april         | august    |
| City           | new-york | marseilles    |
| Flower   | aconite           | orchid   |

